Hi Jon,

April and I have only ever met through the AGS group, so I&#39;ve lacked the opportunity to get led into too much trouble.  I&#39;m up in western Illinois, very near Iowa.  If anyone in the group is going to the AGS conference in Decatur Illinois in June, I&#39;ll be there with a bunch of investigating buddies from Mercer County Paranormal Investigations.

It&#39;s good to meet you!

Barb


